 * @copyright   2012 by iHMS Team
 * @author      Laurent Declercq <l.declercq@nuxwin.com>
 * @version     0.0.1
 * @link        https://github.com/i-HMS/sysconf Sysconf Home Site
 * @license     http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-2.0.html GPL v2
